I want to work in social work with the Division of Family and Children Services. I want to help children who have been hurt or not taken care of. I also want to help families who have problems. My values for social work are: helping others, respecting people, being honest, and working hard to help people and to get better myself. These values are important for social workers and important for me too.

I have always wanted to help others. But I was not sure what job I wanted to do. In high school and college, I saw people running from their problems and using bad ways to deal with them. Because of what I saw, I studied psychology. After I graduated from college in 2009, I took a break. One summer day, a friend introduced me to a 16-year-old boy who was visiting her. He was there to escape his parents. The next day, he called the police. I went to his parents' house to see if I could help. I told the police about my psychology degree and they asked me to talk to the parents. When I talked to them, they seemed nervous and made excuses. After that, I thought about becoming a social worker to help children and families.

Another important value for social work is fairness. We say that every person is special, but we often want to be like everyone else. If we think every person is special, why do we try to be the same as others? I am an individual and I do not like putting limits on myself to be like others. In high school and college, I stood up for what I believe in. I wore colorful hair, wore clothes that fit my personality, and stood up against racism and unfair treatment. I believe in fairness and will keep standing up for what is right.

This paper looks at two models that explain insomnia. The first model is about the biological reasons for insomnia. It considers the role of genetics and medical health. The second model is about how our surroundings and environment affect our health.

The biological model studies the genetics we get from our parents and how our bodies work. It looks at the parts of the brain that control our sleep. A part of the brain called the hypothalamus controls our sleep and wakefulness. Some studies with mice found that a special kind of receptor in the brain helps us sleep. If this receptor is not working correctly, we may not sleep well.

The sociocultural model looks at how our environment and society affect our health. It considers things like our race, where we live, and how much money we have. This model says that our surroundings can affect our sleep. If we have a problem with our sleep, it can affect our daily life. We may have trouble in school, at work, or with everyday tasks.

There are many types of sleep disorders. They can be primary, meaning they are the main problem. Or they can be caused by another health problem or a mental disorder. The primary sleep disorders are called Dyssonmias and Parasomnias. Dyssonmias are problems with falling asleep or staying asleep. Parasomnias are sleep disorders that cause strange behaviors or physical problems. Examples of Dyssonmias include insomnia, where we have trouble sleeping, and hypersomnia, where we are always tired. Parasomnias include sleepwalking and nightmares.

This paper will look at the biological and sociocultural models of insomnia. It will talk about the strengths and weaknesses of the research.

This paper is about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). CAPD is a problem with how the brain uses sound. The brain cannot understand sound correctly. People with CAPD can hear sounds, but they have trouble understanding what they mean.

The earliest study of CAPD was in the 1950s. It was first called "auditory imperception." In the 1960s, researchers started to develop tests to help children with this problem. They wanted to know why the brain was not working correctly.

People with CAPD have trouble with many things. They may not be able to tell where a sound is coming from. They may have trouble hearing two or more sounds at the same time. They may not be able to recognize patterns in sounds. They may not be able to understand speech. One sound may block out another sound. They may not be able to understand what sounds mean.

To diagnose CAPD, doctors and specialists use tests. They watch how the person hears and responds to sounds. They may ask the person to do tasks, like listening to words and numbers. There is no one test that works every time. There is no known cause for CAPD.

A doctor or specialist will look at how the person hears and responds to sounds. They may use special tools to measure the sounds in the ear. They may ask the person to do tasks, like hearing different words or numbers. The goal is to understand how the brain is working with sound.

The play Twelfth Night says that wearing a disguise can be useful for deceiving others. But in the end, a person must stop pretending or lose themselves. Ending a deception can be hard because it can make people not want to be friends with you. So, you must decide between keeping yourself safe or keeping your friends.

Twelfth Night also talks about people who pretend to be the opposite sex. This is a big problem because it raises many questions. For example, why do people feel the need to hide their real selves and pretend to be someone else? Viola does this because she wants to protect herself from danger.

Viola is a woman who pretends to be a man in a new country. She does this to stay safe, but it also makes her feel alone. She is very good at pretending to be a man that even Olivia, a woman, falls in love with her. Viola also has feelings for Orsino, but she is pretending to be a man, so she is unsure what to do.

Some people think that Twelfth Night shows how pretending to be someone else can help people express their true feelings. For example, Olivia and Orsino might have feelings for each other that they don't know about. But others think this might not be true. Olivia seems to be making fun of people who judge others based on how they look.

This is shown by the way Olivia quickly forgets about her love for Orsino and starts to see Viola as a sister.

The German government controlled many lands outside Germany. Many people think this was very cruel. They point to what happened to the Ovaherero and Nama people in South West Africa. The German government did not control all lands the same way. Education in the colonies was also different. 

In East Africa, the British found educated Africans when they took over in 1919. The German government had worked hard to educate the people. People wrote good things about German education in other colonies like Kamerun.

But South West Africa was different. The government did not help much with education. Missionary groups taught the Africans, but they did not have enough money. The government spent a lot on education for Europeans. It built schools for them and helped the missionary schools. This had a big effect on South West Africa for a long time.

Other German colonies had many educated Africans. But in South West Africa, most people were not educated. They were not able to read and write. Many things caused this difference. This paper wants to find out what these things were and how they affected South West Africa. We will look at what the settlers and colonial leaders thought about Africans.

There are many books about education in the German colonies. Most of these books are in German and were written a long time ago. They mainly described the education systems in the colonies. Later books in English compared education in the different colonies and looked at specific parts of education. These studies showed that the colonies had very different education systems.

One important book is by Cohen. He compares education in South West Africa and East Africa. He says the number of European settlers in South West Africa was a big reason for the differences in education. 

South West Africa had a good climate, but much of the land was desert. Many Europeans lived in South West Africa because it was a good place to live. By 1913, over 15,000 Europeans lived there. This was more than in East Africa.

Popular music has many kinds. In the past 100 years, the number of kinds has increased. Many kinds of music have smaller kinds within them. For example, rock music has many kinds, such as heavy metal, country, and folk. Heavy metal music has become very popular in the past 40 years. It expresses many emotions, but it usually shows the darker side of feelings. People who listen to it like its variety. Many people started to make their own kinds of heavy metal music after it came out. Today, it is hard to say what heavy metal music is. It has taken ideas from other kinds of music.

Heavy metal music is a movement. It is defined by its dark feelings. Heavy metal music is louder and more exciting than other kinds of music. People who play it are very good at their instruments. Heavy metal music has a long history. It started many years ago. Some people used drugs to make music that was different and new. Heavy metal music has a bad and emotional sound. It is different from most other kinds of music. The Beatles made a song called Helter Skelter. It is considered one of the first heavy metal songs. The song is about the Beatles' feelings about the Rolling Stones. They wanted to show that they could make heavy music too.

Henri Rousseau was an artist. He painted dreamlike pictures before the Surrealist artists. His famous painting, The Dream, shows a woman visiting a wonderful place in her dream. The painting also shows Rousseau's own dreams and goals.

Rousseau wanted the art world to like his paintings. He wanted artists and art lovers to say nice things about his work. But he had a big problem. He wanted to fit in with the art world, but he also wanted to be different.

To understand The Dream, we need to know about Rousseau's life. He was born on May 21, 1844, in a town in northwest France. His father was a man who sold metal things. Rousseau grew up without learning art in school. He worked for the government until he was 40. He was a man who helped collect money from people who brought goods into the country. People called him a customs inspector.

Rousseau's first wife died. She was followed by the death of their eight baby children. Rousseau was left with one daughter and a lot of sadness. He started painting to feel better. Rousseau is different from other artists. He paints like a regular person, not like the artists who paint beautiful things.

Rousseau wanted to be accepted by the art world. It was hard for him because he started painting late and he was not as famous as other artists. But he worked hard. He did not get recognition until a famous artist named Matisse was already known.

A man named Jan Gordon said that Rousseau and Matisse were different. Rousseau wanted to paint in a simple way so people would like his art. Matisse wanted to paint in a new and interesting way.

Many great thinkers think ethics and beauty are connected. I agree with them. There is a reason for this connection. The poet John Keats said, "Beauty is truth. Truth is beauty." This means that these two things are the same.

We learn many things in life through education and experience. But we seem to like ethics and beauty without being taught. Both ethics and beauty try to explain things, not tell us what to do. We study morality and beauty to understand why something is good or beautiful. We do not have rules to decide what is good or beautiful.

Critics of art or morals can't fully explain what is good or beautiful. A conversation about a famous painting like the Mona Lisa might talk about things like color and shape. But these things don't explain why the painting is good. When people talk about their favorite art or literature, they often say, "There's just something about it." This means there is something special that can't be explained.

I think art and morals are the same in this way. As the writer Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that can't be said any other way." We can't fully describe the qualities of a work of art or literature. There is always something more.

I think ethics and art are closely related because they both touch our souls in a deep way. This connection is especially strong with literature. The writer McKean said, "What makes literature special is its moral quality." Literature helps us understand values, which are important for living.

Germany is a strong and united country. It has its own special culture from the Alps to the Baltic Sea. From the city of München to the city of Kiel, you can feel this culture. It is also found along the Rhine River in Köln and in the city of Dresden.

Germany's culture comes from many different people and tribes. People have argued about where the country got its name for a long time. Some say it came from a group of people known as the Tungrians. They were a Germanic tribe. They lived in the area before they moved to the other side of the Rhine River.

The Roman leader Julius Caesar wrote about the Germans. He used the word "Germanus" to talk about them. He got the word from the Gauls. The Gauls used it to describe their neighbors. Caesar used it to talk about the people he fought against.

Caesar wrote that the Germans lived beyond the Rhine River. He said they were always fighting the Gauls. He said they used spears in battle. Some people think the name "German" comes from this spear. Others think it comes from the sound of the Germanic tribes making a loud noise.

The Roman historian Tacitus wrote about the Germans in his book. He said they were an original people. He said they were not mixed with other groups of people. He said people would not choose to move from other countries to live in Germany because it was a difficult place.

The Romans did trade with the Germanic tribes. They also went to Germany to fight. But they mostly went home after that. The Germanic tribes traded goods and skills with the Romans. They also fought with the Romans.

I looked down.  I did not think about what I saw.  It was just a picture in front of me.  I saw a bowl of fruit on a table.  But it was hard to understand the picture.

I read a book on art.  The book is called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain."  The book teaches how to draw.  It says to put a square frame around the picture you want to draw.  This makes the picture simple.

I tried to put a frame around what I saw, but I could not.  I was too busy looking at the bowl.  I was amazed.

I thought about artists who loved different colors.  Picasso liked blue.  Monet liked green.  But I liked brown.  I wanted to create something good.

I picked up a pencil.  My hand moved.  I wanted to make something beautiful.  But my hand moved to the toilet instead.  I was trying to fix the toilet, not draw.

I cleaned the toilet.  I was not happy.  There was a big piece of waste in the toilet.  I was annoyed.  I wanted to get rid of it.  I flushed the toilet several times.  I still could not get rid of it.

I took some toilet paper.  I wrapped it around my hand.  I put my hand in the toilet.  I wanted to get the waste out.  I felt like I was cooking a turkey in an oven.

Teenagers are dying while driving. Many things cause this problem. The National Institutes of Health say one reason is that the teen brain is not ready for the dangers of driving. Teenagers also have little driving experience. This experience causes many deaths and accidents. 

When teens drive with their friends, they are more likely to have accidents. A study by the Southern California Injury Prevention Research Center shows that passengers under 20 years old make more accidents. 

California and other states try to make driving safer for teenagers by giving them temporary licenses. These licenses limit when they can drive and who can ride with them. 

But, I think these licenses are not enough. The real problem is that teenagers as a group cannot handle driving risks and responsibilities. A psychologist named Marvin Zuckerman says 18 is too young for a regular license. He says people under 19-20 years old often want to take risks for fun. We should delay driving until this tendency to take risks goes away. If we give licenses to young teens, we will see more accidents and many deaths. 

By 2010, many new teen drivers will be on the road. Schools can teach driver's education classes, but no one under 18 can drive. A provisional license can still be given before a full license. Drivers must practice for a certain number of hours with an adult. The number of hours can be the same as other states. This law would help all states, not just California. It is a simple way to protect teenagers. Many states already have this law. It is not a new idea.

I looked at the Library of Congress's old movies by Thomas Edison. I saw fifteen trick films from 1895 to 1901. These films use creative editing to create illusions.

I studied the trick films. I looked at the way most of them are made and the special features of a few later ones. Most trick films from that time are set in one place. They use one camera angle and no movement. They use long and medium shots and show only one thing at a time. However, some early films break these rules by using more than one shot.

All trick films have some things in common. They are filmed in a set that looks like a stage. The camera does not move to follow the people or objects. This style comes from the theatre and stage shows. It has its roots in magic acts. Because of this style, people in the films only move from side to side. They do not walk towards or away from the camera. For example, look at the film "Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel" from 1900. The actors enter from one side and move back and forth.

The way the camera sees the scene is also the same. It usually shows long shots and sometimes medium shots. Close-up shots are never used in these films. This is like a theatre, where the audience sees everything on the stage. The actors do not move towards the camera, so close-up shots are not used.

Most early trick films are short. They usually last one minute or less. They also focus on tricks like magic and disappearing. However, sometimes one shot can be many joined together to create an illusion. For example, look at the film "The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots" from 1895. One part of the film looks like one shot, but it is actually many shots joined together.

John Taylor was a man who believed in freedom.  He was a farmer and a politician.  He wanted people to have freedom and be able to make their own choices.  He thought a farm was the best job.  He wanted a government that helped farmers.

John Taylor thought the United States was a great place to make a perfect system of government.  No one in America had a tradition of how to make a government, so they could try something new.  He believed people have rights that should be protected.  If one right is taken away, all rights are less valuable.  He thought the government should not control these rights.

Taylor believed some people are strong and clever.  In a wild state, they have power.  But in a country, this is not right.  He said a government should be made to understand good and bad in people.  He believed in two kinds of goodness and badness.  He said a good government should protect property, help farmers, and not favor rich people.  He thought a good government would be fair, no matter who was in charge.  But he knew people in charge would often be selfish.  He said people are selfish, but it is wrong to be selfish when it hurts others.

Taylor wanted a small government.  He did not want the government to have more powers than the Constitution said it could have.  He thought a big government would be expensive and unfair.  But he also thought a simple interpretation of the Constitution could be wrong.  He thought the Declaration of Independence was more important than the Constitution because it said the United States was a group of states, not one country.

We look at Figure 17. The number of commuter logs in the third month of the project went down. This was a problem. We do not know why this happened. It may be because of winter. In New England, people do not ride bicycles or walk as much in the winter. This can explain some of the decrease. December is a busy time for students and teachers. They are working hard and finishing schoolwork. They may forget to fill out the commuter log. This is also the time of year when students and teachers have a long break for the holidays. They do not need to come to campus. Classes start again in January. This may also explain the low number of logs in January. But the number of logs in February is still low. We can think of a few reasons for this. One reason is that people may lose interest in a project after a while. This is normal. To solve this problem, we started a special project called Carpool Challenge Week. It was a week of activity in March. We wanted to make people interested again. And it worked. The number of logs went up in March. We learned that one of the challenges of this project is that people like to drive their cars. This is a part of our culture. We need to give them a reason to use other ways to travel. We gave out prizes to people who used public transportation or carpools. The prizes were gift cards to restaurants, coffee shops, and stores. It would be good to know how big prizes would affect participation. For example, giving away a bicycle or a new car might make people more interested in using public transportation. We did not change the prizes during the project. If we had announced bigger prizes, like bicycles or cars, at the beginning of December and January, people might have been more interested and participated more.

An ETF is a security that tracks a group or a thing, like a stock.  But it is more flexible and can be sold quickly like a stock.  An ETF gives you the good things of many stocks and the good things of owning one stock.  You can sell it short, buy more with a loan, and buy just a little.  The cost of an ETF is lower than a mutual fund.  But there are some bad things, like paying a fee to buy or sell.  There are many kinds of ETFs to choose from.  But you must check if an ETF really does what it says it will do.

We will look at the ETF IHF.  We will compare it to the top 10 stocks that make up the ETF.  We want to see if buying the 10 stocks is better than buying the ETF.  We want to know if there are better ways to buy these stocks.

We will only look at the top 10 stocks that make up 63.58% of the ETF.  Here are the top 10 stocks and how much of the ETF they make up.

To see how well the 10 stocks represent the ETF, we will use a special method.  We will calculate the Beta and Return of a portfolio made up of the 10 stocks in the same amount as the ETF.

The chart shows that the return of the 10 stocks is 6.11% higher than the ETF.  This is a 16% increase in returns.  The Beta of the 10 stocks is 0.12 lower than the ETF.  This means that the 10 stocks might give a higher return with less risk.

But we need to know if these results are real.  So we will calculate the standard deviation of the 10 stocks and compare it to the ETF.

Edgar Allan Poe wrote a famous poem called "Dream-Land." It is one of his best poems. Poe uses the word "Thule" in his poem. He got this word from Virgil, a famous writer from a long time ago. Virgil used the word "Thule" to name an island near Britain. The Greeks thought this island was the end of the known world. 

Poe liked to read books by German writers. One of these writers was Goethe. Goethe wrote a poem called "Faust." It has two parts. In the second part, there is a short poem called "The King of Thule." The poem is about a king who loses his wife. He is very sad and starts drinking. He decides to die and leaves his possessions to his children. The poem is about a man who is very sad and unhappy.

Goethe's poem "Faust" is very famous. Poe probably read it. Poe used the word "Thule" in two of his poems. He used it at the beginning and end of "Dream-Land." This shows that Poe was thinking about Goethe's poem. The two poems are like two parts of the same story. In "Dream-Land," the speaker is in a dark and lonely place. He sees dead friends and a world without color. This is like the king in Goethe's poem. The king has lost his wife and is very sad.

Goethe was a very important writer. Poe probably read his work. Poe liked Alfred Tennyson, another famous writer. Poe said he admired Tennyson. Poe would have read Goethe's work because of his respect for Tennyson. Many people were copying Goethe's books after they were first published. This means Poe probably read Goethe's work.

A customer named Jennifer Palmer slipped and fell in a grocery store called D&D Markets. She fell because of a big spill of applesauce on the floor. Now, she wants money for her injury. The money is called punitive damages. To get this money, Palmer must show that the store manager, Mr. Martin, acted very badly. He knew about the spill, but he did not clean it up. He was eating dinner at the time.

A judge will not quickly dismiss Palmer's claim. To get punitive damages, Palmer must show that Mr. Martin acted on purpose to hurt her. He must have known that his actions would cause harm. Mr. Martin's actions were not good, but they were not very good either. Six customers had slipped and fallen in the store in the past year. Mr. Martin knew this, but he did not take care to make the store safe.

On October 13, 2009, at 5:00 pm, an employee named Rich Wayne told Mr. Martin about the applesauce spill. Mr. Martin said he was busy eating dinner and did not have time to deal with the problem. At 5:15 pm, another employee, Mary J. Haddigan, also told Mr. Martin about the spill. He said the same thing. At 5:30 pm, Palmer slipped and fell. Before that, five other customers had slipped and fallen in the store.

In California, a person can get punitive damages if someone acts very badly. The law says "bad" means doing something on purpose to hurt someone, or not doing something that would help someone even if you know it will hurt them. A court said that someone is acting badly if they know something will hurt someone, and they do not try to stop it.

Four years ago, I took a course in Islam at CBC.  We talked about a big question: is Islam a harmful religion?  I think this question is more important now than ever.  After 9/11, the news about Islam changed.  It used to be mostly bad news, but now it is more positive.  In 2001, a man named Barack Obama was not a likely candidate for president because he comes from a Muslim family.

I read the story of the Prophet Muhammad.  What I learned is different from what I expected.  I thought Muhammad forced people to become Muslim.  He would win battles and make the people change their religion.  But the story says Muhammad was a kind person.  He was misunderstood and humble.  People came to believe in him because of his good teaching.

There are some interesting similarities between the stories of Jesus and Muhammad.  One example is when Muhammad had some food and made it multiply so that there was enough for forty people.  The writers of the story want us to see Muhammad as a humble prophet who did not need to prove anything.  This is a problem because it takes away from the miracles of Jesus.

The story of Muhammad has many events that show people becoming Muslim.  But the problem is that these stories are not from direct witnesses.  They are from people who heard from others who heard from others.  I did not like this because it makes the stories seem less real.

The main problem with the story of Muhammad is that it makes him a godly man who is humble and kind.  But history says Muhammad was not always humble.  I think Muslims should know the real story of Muhammad's rise to power.

The teachings of Jesus and his beliefs were not preserved in the growth of Christian thought after his death.  Let us look at this story in simple terms.  As time passed, Christianity moved away from its start.  Today, people are more aware and open to change.  Some people continue to follow old ideas, but they are not many.  Many Christians will understand the past better in the future.  People will want to know the difference between ideas added to Christianity and Jesus' true message.  This will take a long time, but the result will be clear:  Christianity will return to its original form.  A movement will grow that will remove new ideas, one by one.  Eventually, only Jesus' simple ideas will remain.  When this happens in America and Europe, many people will follow Jesus' ideas, just like in his time.  The church will still be strong, but people will believe and act the same way everywhere.

We see this kind of change in history.  For example, the Roman Empire persecuted Christians, but later it became Christian.  Our country used to be very unfair to African-Americans, but now they have leaders.  In the future, Christianity will go back to its roots and become simpler.  This will happen because people will understand Jesus' words as examples, not as exact words.  So, what happened to Jesus' ideas after his time?

Looking back, we see only Judaism, the start of the Christian religion.  At that time, the Jewish people had one God and believed in the Bible.  But the Jewish people were not all the same.  They were divided into groups like Sadducees, Pharisees, Essenes, and Zealots, and many others.

In The Jungle, Upton Sinclair shows how people are naturally selfish. They only think of themselves and want to make their lives better. They do not think about others. The Jungle shows this in many ways. 

One way is with the owners and managers of big factories. They want to make their companies and factories bigger and more successful. They do not care about anyone or anything that gets in their way. Sinclair writes about the pollution caused by factories. He says it is very bad and hurts people and animals.

The owners and managers also do not care about their workers. They are very mean to them. They make the workers work very long hours and then often fire them without notice. This is very unfair. In the time when the book is set, there were no laws to protect workers. This means the owners and managers could do whatever they wanted.

Many workers died because of the bad working conditions. There was no help for them. Some workers formed groups to protect themselves, but these groups often made money from the workers. The workers were very unhappy and had no way to escape their bad situation. They were treated like slaves.

Sinclair writes that in this situation, bad things happen. People are treated unfairly and do bad things to each other. This is like when slaves were treated badly a long time ago.

Many authors try to make readers feel a certain way about important subjects. They use different methods to do this. Some methods are better than others. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many of these methods in his book 'The Great Gatsby'.

Fitzgerald uses an adjective and a noun together to create a certain feeling. He uses this method with colors like gold, green, white and red. He makes these colors mean something special. Later, he uses these colors to remind readers of a feeling.

In 'The Great Gatsby', Fitzgerald makes white and gray mean the same thing. He thinks white is better and higher class. Gray is older and faded. He uses these colors in the beginning of the book to make this point.

Daisy and Jordan wear white a lot. Everyone is wearing white at one point. When people are not wearing white, it's when Nick is thinking about Gatsby's party. The party is colorful.

Fitzgerald makes white and gray mean more than just colors. He uses them for common things too. He describes the city as having white and gray. He says Daisy and Jordan had a white childhood together. There are gray cars and land in the valley.

Fitzgerald adds more meaning to white and gray, and then uses them to show that something is not important. He starts with Daisy. After a long time without using these colors, Fitzgerald says Daisy is wearing white. Readers see her as not special, but like something Gatsby wants.

Fitzgerald uses this method again and again to make readers see Daisy as not special. He says she has a gray fur collar, and she wears white before Gatsby and Tom meet.

San Diego County is a good place for growing food. The weather is mild and sunny. It is good for growing many types of food like tomatoes, citrus fruits, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, and fruits from trees like peaches and lemons. Many people also grow berries and peppers. There is a big demand for organic food in San Diego. Many local groups want to buy food from local farms. These groups have a long list of people waiting to buy from them. Many organic farms also sell eggs and milk. Some of these farms let people visit to see how they grow food. People can also walk, look at birds, and do other fun activities on these farms.

This type of farm is good for the landowner. It helps the landowner get money from government programs. It also helps the land. This makes the land better for animals and people. The landowner can also have fun and teach others about farming.

Growing organic food has many benefits. The plants and animals around the farm are healthy. This is because the soil and water are clean. However, growing organic food is more expensive in some ways. It takes more work to get rid of bad bugs and weeds. It also takes more work to make the soil healthy without using chemicals. The farm may lose more food than a big farm. A small organic farm is also not as efficient as a big farm.

Some things the landowner does to help the animals may cost more money. These things include planting special crops to help the soil, moving animals to different areas, removing bad plants, and making sure the plants grow in the right way.

I chose a piece of land near the town of Potrero in San Diego County, California. It is 160 acres of land with chaparral, grass, and oak trees. It is near a big forest. Many plants and animals live there. Some are in danger of disappearing. I looked at a real estate website and found government programs that can help a small farmer. I also looked at an organic farm in the same area to see what a farmer might do on this land.

Culture is very important in any negotiation. Culture is not one thing. It can be different at different times and in different places. We should not say all people from one country are the same. For example, it is not true that all Russians are stubborn or that all Japanese are friendly. 

When we meet a new culture, we see it in relation to our own culture. This creates comparisons. To understand a new culture, we can study its past or its values. Instead of judging a culture, we should accept it as it is. This is especially true during a negotiation. If we have a weak position in a negotiation, showing respect for a culture can be very helpful. 

A culture is not just about a country. Companies have their own culture too. A company's culture can be strict or relaxed. We can see a company's culture in how employees dress, how they talk, and how they work together. Some companies like employees to help others, while others do not allow it. We can see big differences in corporate culture even within the same country. 

It is also important to understand what a culture values. Values help us know why people behave in certain ways. If a culture values saving face, a negotiator will not shame their company or superior to get what they want. If a culture values a hard bargain, a negotiator will not settle easily. Knowing these values can help us before we go into a negotiation. However, we should also try to learn about the other person's personal values to make the negotiation more effective.

A man said, "There is no God." This is found in the Bible. Two men, St. Anselm and Thomas Aquinas, wrote about the existence of God. We will compare their ideas. To make it easy to compare, we will assume both are correct that God exists.

St. Anselm's idea is that we can find God in our own minds. He says we cannot think of God not existing. This means the proof of God is inside us. We do not need outside help to know God exists. This idea is called faith. Faith is believing something without proof.

Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He thinks we can prove God exists with reason and facts. We do not need faith. He uses five arguments to prove God exists. They are change, cause, chance, good things, and harmony. He says these things are like a puzzle. If you have most of the puzzle pieces, you can know what the missing piece is.

Long ago, in the fifth or sixth century before Christ, a prince named Buddha was born. He became an important teacher. At some point in his life, he left the world and found inner peace. His teachings made a new religion. This religion is called Buddhism. The most traditional kind of Buddhism is called Theravada Buddhism. It is around 2,500 years old. Today, it is not the same as it was when Buddha lived.

People can see the changes everywhere. For example, in Sri Lanka, a country with many Theravada Buddhists, there is a special ceremony called the water-cutting ceremony. Many people, both monks and ordinary people, take part in this ceremony. It is an important event, even though Buddha never taught about it. These changes occur in many areas, from small customs to the main ideas of the religion. Over time, the Theravada Buddhist community has changed its main ideas. This happened because of many reasons, both good and bad.

In this discussion, we will use some important words. An internal force is a change that comes from someone who is a Buddhist. An external force is a change that comes from someone who is not a Buddhist. A hostile force is a change that hurts the Buddhist community. A benign force is a change that does not hurt the Buddhist community, but it may do so by accident.

First, we need to learn about the main ideas of Theravada Buddhism. Buddhists believe in three important things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is the teachings of the Buddha. These teachings are in three groups: the Sutta Pitaka, the Vinaya Pitaka, and the Abhidhamma Pitaka. The Sutta Pitaka has many important teachings. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for living. The Abhidhamma Pitaka has ideas about the world. Some of these ideas are that everything is not permanent and that life has suffering.

To end suffering, we must understand these ideas. We must also understand that attachment causes suffering. If we can understand these ideas, we can end the cycle of death and rebirth. We can also end desire, hatred, and delusion. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for living. For lay people, there are five main rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not be immoral, and do not take bad substances. For monks, there are many more rules. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. First, life is suffering. Second, attachment causes suffering. Third, we can end suffering.

The United States and Mexico had a long rivalry that lasted 57 years.  This started in 1836 and ended in 1893.  The high point of this rivalry was the Mexican-American War from 1846 to 1848.  The United States won this war and got Texas and the American Southwest as new land.  There were many problems between the two countries, but they became smaller just before World War I.

The United States and Mexico had disagreements on important issues like religion and culture.  They also had disagreements on money and wealth.  This is true for many countries with a shared border.  When countries share a border, they often disagree on things.  This can cause problems between the countries.

The United States and Mexico are not alone in their long-standing problems.  Cuba is another country the United States had problems with.  David M. Pletcher said that the United States had big diplomatic problems with these two countries for a long time.  Both countries are near the United States, but they have been rivals.  Other countries in Latin America have good relationships with the United States.

Religion was a big problem between the United States and Mexico.  Sally Frahm said that Americans were against Catholicism and the monarchy in the 18th and 19th centuries.  This was like the Cold War between the United States and the Soviet Union.  In that case, the disagreement was about politics and interests.  But with the United States and Mexico, the disagreement was about religion.

The distrust between the United States and Mexico started with the English and Spanish.  This distrust was passed down from their former rulers.  This made it hard for the two countries to be friends.

The United States and Mexico had 17 problems in the 57-year period of their rivalry.  Most of these problems were about land and border conflicts.  Some of these conflicts were caused by bandits and outlaws from American towns on the border.  Both countries had to use military force to stop these problems.  The rivalry between the United States and Mexico finally ended when Mexico became dependent on the United States and the United States changed its goals from taking land to helping Mexico economically.

Fifteen years ago, I got very sick. I had no idea it would happen. I was a nurse at the time. I chose nursing because I wanted a safe job. People always need help when they are sick.

I wanted to be a scientist or a journalist when I grew up. But I chose nursing instead. I wanted to help people. Now, I am 46 years old, single, and I have no money. I get help from the government because I am sick. But I have no money left.

Every day is hard for me. I am not safe, and I do not feel good about myself. But I have family and friends who help me. They are my friends because they care about me. When bad things happen, we need help from others.

We should not count on the government for everything. The government is not always strong. We need to help each other. We need to trust each other. We can learn from our past. Our ancestors in America were brave. They came to America in wagons. They had a hard time, but they helped each other.

We should be prepared for bad things. I have supplies in case of an emergency. I have water, food, and a first aid kit. But the most important thing is to know your neighbors. They can help you when you need it.

Why do living things change over time? Are there rules that influence how they change? In 1917, D'Arcy Thompson said that it is hard to use math to understand even simple living things. This is still true today. Recently, people have used math to study how shells grow in mollusks. Our study is trying to use math and experiments to learn how shells change over time in a group of animals called Prunum. We used special pictures of Prunum shells to find numbers that can help us understand how shells grow. We put these numbers into a computer program to see how shells might look in the past or future. We combined this with other studies to learn more about how Prunum shells changed over time.

A shell is like a tube that moves around in a circle. This circle is called a spiral. The spiral has many parts that grow in a line. Each part is called a whorl. A line in the middle of the shell is called the columella. The whorls can grow at different speeds. A line between each whorl is called a suture. The biggest whorl is the last one. The part before the last whorl is called the spire. The tip of the spire is called the apex. The other end is called the base. The animal comes out of its shell through an opening called the aperture.

We can look at shells from different angles. These angles are called apical, basal, apertural, and abapertural views. The usual way to look at a shell is from the apertural view. 

To count the whorls, we look at the shell from the top. We find the first line between whorls, then draw a line across the shell. We count the whorls from this line. We can also estimate the number of whorls.

A shell is like a path that the animal follows as it grows. We can follow this path by looking at the center of each whorl and the size of the opening. We can show this path with math and pictures. Once we have the math, we can change the numbers to see how the shell might look in the past or future.

In Indonesia, many babies and children die in their first year. This has not changed much in the last ten years. Indonesia is doing well in some areas, like making clean water and sanitation better. But it is not doing well in areas that affect the health of mothers and children.

More babies are born with a trained helper. Now 72% of births have a skilled worker present. But this number includes traditional helpers, like midwives. They cannot help if a pregnancy problem happens. This means that many mothers still die from heavy bleeding during birth.

The number of sick children getting medical help for diarrhea is going down. But we do not have good information about how well new mothers are taking care of themselves after giving birth. In some areas, this is a big problem.

Only a few mothers have a Cesarean-section, which is a surgery to help during birth. The rate of Cesarean-section is higher in cities than in rural areas. This shows that people in cities have better access to healthcare. People in rural areas have a hard time getting the help they need.

The poor have a hard time getting healthcare. They cannot afford to pay out of pocket. There is a big gap in healthcare use between the richest and poorest people.

We need to think about how to make healthcare better for mothers and babies. One idea is to make the healthcare system stronger. This means making sure all areas of healthcare are working well, not just one area. But this can be hard to do. It takes time and money.

One way to make things better is to focus on one area and work on that. This can make things happen faster. But there are problems with this idea. If we give a lot of money to one area, other areas might not get enough money. And people might not want to work in areas that need help.

We need to think carefully about how to make healthcare better for mothers and babies in Indonesia.

Victorian books are known for their great details. They often talk about the rich people of that time. Two books that do not follow this rule are Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights. These books use mystery and strange ideas. This makes the characters in the book better. It helps us understand their feelings and what they want.

One part of Oliver Twist is like a dream. Oliver sees and hears things that are not real. He sees two men, Sikes and Crackit, who are fighting. He hears their voices, but he does not know what is real and what is not. He is in pain and does not know what is happening.

In this book, Oliver has many strange experiences. These help us understand what is inside Oliver's heart. When Oliver is shot, he sees it again in his mind. He is trying to find help. Oliver does not have control over what happens to him. He is in a lot of pain and is very scared.

This makes us wonder who is causing Oliver's troubles. It was not Oliver's fault. He does not try to control what happens to him, even when his life is in danger. This shows that Oliver is giving up. He is losing hope.

Another part of the book says: "The day went by - but there was no day. It came and went quickly. Night came and it was very quiet, but it was also very short."

Two years ago, I worked in an after-school program helping students who needed extra help with their studies. I helped students with their problems, but I was good at helping with English and reading. One of the instructors asked me to help a boy named Adrian. He was in the third or fourth grade and was having trouble reading. Something strange was happening with Adrian. Some letters he knew how to say, but others he did not. He spoke English very well, but his family was Latino. I was helping the other students on a field trip when his mother came in. She did not speak English, only Spanish. We talked in Spanish a little. Then I understood the problem. Adrian knew how to read, but he did not know the English alphabet. I hope he is doing better now.

I tell this story to talk about a big problem in schools, especially in California. This problem is that some students do not speak much English. Even if they speak English, reading can be hard for them. Everyone agrees that this is a problem. What can we do about it? In Adrian's case, I helped him with English reading. But for other students who do not speak much English, it is harder to solve the problem. There is no single answer. We need to use many ways to help. These are dual language programs, immersion classes, private tutors, and English classes for students who do not speak English well. We should use all of these things together.

First, dual language programs are a good idea. They help all students, not just those who speak Spanish at home. Many studies have shown that students in these programs do better in school. Some people are afraid that these programs are a waste of money. They think most students will not benefit. But this is not true. If we use these programs in all schools, all students will benefit. How can we do this? Do we need all teachers to speak two languages? No, that is not possible or reasonable. But we can have special helpers who speak two languages.

When we are young, we learn about something bigger than ourselves.  Some people go to school to learn about it.  Others look inside themselves for the answers.  Many people accept the ideas of their parents.  But some people do not agree.  They think there is no more to life than what we can see and feel.  We search for answers to help us understand the world.

My father liked birds.  "The cardinal," he said when I asked him about his favorite bird.  We sat on our front porch, listening to the rain.  The rain made the plants by the porch get wet.  My father looked out into the rain.  He was thin and his hair was thinning.  He was not looking at me.  I was scared and did not know what to do.  I hugged him and sat back down.  We sat together, looking out at the rain.

My father died in December when I was 22 years old.  The doctors had given up hope.  He was in a lot of pain, but he lived a little longer because of the treatments.  I did not want to watch him die.  I wanted to remember my father as he was, not as he was when he was sick.  I knew my father better than anyone else.  He would not have wanted me to see him die.  I stayed in bed for three days, waiting for the news.  Nobody called me.

The Gothic Novel is a strange mix of old and new ideas. This is what Ian Watt says in his book "The Rise of the Gothic Novel". Many people have criticized or praised this kind of writing. Some say it is not deep, but others see it as very powerful. The writer Horace Walpole created the first Gothic Novel, "The Castle of Otranto". He used old ideas from romance stories and new ideas from modern novels to make a new kind of writing. He wanted to show what he called "A Gothic Story".

The Gothic Novel uses old and new things together. It has elements from medieval theater, architecture, and traditions. When "The Castle of Otranto" was first published, the word "gothic" was used to describe many things. Some people thought it was old-fashioned and not sophisticated. But the combination of old and new ideas made the Gothic Novel special and kept it alive for a long time.

One important idea in Gothic Novels is chivalry. This is a medieval idea about how to train a knight. It is about being brave, honorable, and competent. The writer Horace Walpole liked this idea because it represented a perfect knight. He wanted to show that this kind of person was not present in society anymore. He was writing during a difficult time in politics and was unhappy about the future.

Walpole's character Frederic is a good example of this idea. He is a prince who has suffered and is brave. He is described as a gallant and courteous knight. This is an exaggeration of the ideal knight, which is a common theme in Gothic writing. It shows how writers of that time wanted to create a better image of society.

Supply chain management is a process. It is the process of moving things from raw materials to finished products. We get the raw materials. We make the products. We send them to customers. The person who invented the term supply chain management is Keith Oliver. He is a consultant. He explained how to plan, implement, and control the process to satisfy customers' needs quickly and efficiently.

There are six key parts to a supply chain. They are production, supply, inventory, location, transportation, and information. Business managers use these six key parts to give good service to customers.

Production is the first step in the supply chain process. It is the base of the supply chain. Production is when and how we make things. Managers need to know what customers want. They can look at the market to find out. The market tells us what customers want to buy.

Managers have to decide what to produce and how much to produce. They also have to decide where to make the products. They choose a place that can make the products quickly and with good quality. The customer's needs and wants must be met.

The next step is to schedule work and take care of equipment. Production is a very important part of the supply chain. Every detail is important. If we do not plan well, it can cost us time and money.

A good example is Wal-Mart and Target. They have a plan for every part of their business. They have a plan for how employees dress and how to receive shipments. This helps them work smoothly and on time.

The second key part of supply chain management is supply. Supply is making strategic decisions about what a company can do well and what it should do with others. A company may have many groups working on the same product. The manager decides which group is best for each job. They may also decide to work with other companies to save time and money. This is called velocity. It means giving good quality and flexibility while keeping costs low.

A sign in Burma, or Myanmar, says a surprising thing: "Hitler is alive here."

Ellen Page, a famous actress, holds a sign above her head on a street corner. The sign has a message written on it with a Sharpie. Burma is a country in Southeast Asia. It is ruled by a military government that took power in 1962. In 2007, people in the streets began to protest. These protests were led by Buddhist monks. The name "Saffron Revolution" was given to these protests, because the monks wear orange robes. At first, the government allowed the monks to gather peacefully. But soon, violence happened. Many people, including a Japanese journalist named Kenji Nagai, were hurt or killed. The death toll is 13, but a former soldier said many more people were killed.

This is not the first time a government has tried to stop people from speaking out. Many governments throughout history have done this. For example, in ancient Rome, the emperor said he was chosen by the gods to rule. In Japan, the emperor is considered a god. And our current president has meetings with leaders of groups who believe they have the right to rule.

Other examples include the Tiananmen Square protest in China in 1989. Students, workers, and intellectuals protested against the government. The death toll is not clear, but it was at least 200. Another example is the Rwandan genocide in the 1990s. Hutu groups killed Tutsis and others. Hitler's rule in Germany is also a bad example of a government trying to control its people.

Duke Ellington's work in jazz is very important. He lived a long time and used his music skills to make his band great. He was not always on the piano in his songs. But he was a good composer. He created many complex and interesting pieces that showed what each band member could do.

Ellington made a plan for the band to play together. He wrote music that allowed each member to play freely. He also wrote music that worked well with the style of each member. This made the band sound better and more original. Ellington knew how each player sounded and how they worked together. This helped him write some of the best jazz music ever.

The Grove Music dictionary talks about Ellington's sound and innovation. It says he used voice like a musical instrument. This is shown in his song Creole Love Call. In this song, Ellington used voice to add feeling and color to the music. He also showed that he could work well with his soloists. Creole Love Call is a slow, blues song with six parts. Here are the parts:

Part 1: Voice and instruments talk to each other. The voice starts smooth and then gets a little rough.
Part 2: A trumpet plays a solo that adds to the melody.
Part 3: A clarinet plays a long, high sound with a special piano pattern.
Part 4: The whole band repeats Part 1.
Part 5: The reeds make the sound and the brass and rhythm sections play a special beat.
Part 6: The song goes back to Part 1. This time the voice sounds like a special effect.

The last part of the song is a short tag with a special sound and a surprising ending.

Ellington used voice to add color to his music. This is one way he made his music special.

In another song, Hot and Bothered, Ellington worked well with his band. He used his skills to make the music sound good and he used the singer's voice to add color. In another song, It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing), Ellington used a trombone player to make the song sound great.

She felt something was missing. This feeling did not go away. It started when she was 14 years old. She was still thinking about it 3 years later, at 17. She decided she wanted a person, not a thing. But she did not like any boys. Some boys liked her, but she did not feel the same. She thought about this a lot. She wanted to know why this was happening to her.

Her family life was usually calm. Her parents were nice people. They never argued. They did not argue with her often. They argued when she wanted more freedom. She liked being different from them. They were calm, but she was fun and nice.

Today was not a calm day. She ran from room to room looking for ideas. She heard her mother's voice in the kitchen. It sounded like she was in pain. She ran to the kitchen and said, "Mom, what's wrong?" She saw her mother on the ground. She said "Ow" many times. She went to her mother and put her hand on her arm. Her mother said, "Ouch, sweetie, take me to the hospital." Her mother's daughter helped her mother to the car.

At the hospital, the air smelled bad. But she was worried about her mother. She carried her mother to a bed and called for doctors. The doctors came and helped her mother. They took her to see a doctor right away. The daughter sat down, waiting.

Her mother fell from a high cabinet while getting a vase. She did not see her mother fall, but she heard her cry in pain.

This study wanted to see if eating a special diet called the "Mediterranean Diet" can help lower the risk of getting serious heart disease and having a stroke. The Mediterranean Diet is a healthy eating plan with many fruits, vegetables, whole grains, and healthy fats.

Earlier studies showed that eating this diet can help lower the risk of death from heart disease. But these studies did not look at how it affects the risk of stroke.

This study followed 74,886 women between 38 and 63 years old. They were all nurses and had not had heart disease or diabetes. The women were part of a larger group of 121,700 nurses. The researchers looked at how well each woman ate by sending them questionnaires about their food every six years from 1984 to 2004. Most of the women answered the questionnaires all 20 years.

The researchers used these questionnaires to give each woman a score for eating the Mediterranean Diet. They also looked at other things that could affect the results, such as weight, smoking, and exercise. They used a special math method to take these things into account.

The study found that women who ate more of the Mediterranean Diet had a lower risk of getting heart disease and having a stroke. Over 20 years, 2,391 women got heart disease, 1,763 got a stroke, and 1,077 died from heart disease or a stroke. Women who ate the most of the Mediterranean Diet had a lower risk of getting heart disease and a stroke compared to those who ate the least.

In 2007, big financial problems came to the United States. Many people lost their jobs, the housing market failed, and many big companies lost a lot of money. This big problem continues today. We must ask: how did this happen and how can we stop it? The financial problem started when banks and companies made bad loans to people who could not pay them back. This was because of bad choices made by politicians. They wanted banks and companies to give loans to people who could not afford them. This was a problem because the country's financial system was not strong enough.

Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac were two big companies that helped make these loans. They took the bad loans and turned them into new kinds of investments. When people who took the loans could not pay them back, the banks lost a lot of money. They gave this problem to the investments they had made. This made a big problem for the whole economy.

This problem started many years ago, in 1999. President Clinton wanted to be re-elected. To do this, he made it easier for people to get loans. He wanted to help more people buy homes. But this made a big problem. A man named Steven Holmes wrote in the New York Times: "Fannie Mae is a big company that helps people get mortgages. The government is pushing Fannie Mae to give loans to people who cannot pay them back." Holmes knew this would cause big problems in the future.

Many things made the problem worse. Some loans were adjustable, meaning the interest rate could change. Other loans were attached to other loans, making it harder to know who owed what. This made the whole economy unstable. People and banks had too much money tied up in the housing market. When the housing market fell, they lost a lot of money.

The housing market burst, and the banks that had bought these bad loans lost a lot of money. The top five banks in the United States had $4.1 trillion in bad loans in 2007. This was 30% of the country's total money. Two big banks, Bear Sterns and Merrill Lynch, were sold cheap. Lehman Brothers went out of business, and two other banks, Goldman Sachs and Morgan Stanley, had to become regular banks with strict rules. Fannie and Freddie had $5 trillion in bad loans and were taken over by the government in 2008.

Exposition is a problem for many writers.  It is the part of a story where you tell the reader too much.  This can make the reader bored or want to stop reading.

You already know the writing rule: "Show, don't tell."  But sometimes writers write too much.  They tell the reader about a character's past, their family, or their feelings.  This is called exposition.

Exposition is when you tell the reader something that happened.  It is like a character telling another character a lot of information.  In movies, this is called a "core-dump."

Let's look at an example.  Imagine a reader learns that a main character met her husband at a certain place and time.  She married him in a beautiful way, and he was killed in front of her.  The reader does not want to read two pages of just this information.  The reader wants to know about the husband's character.  How did he feel about his wife?  How did she feel about him?

A good writer will show this with the characters' words and actions.  This makes the reader care about the characters and feel sad when something bad happens.  The reader will feel connected to the main character.

So, a good story has more than just the main events.  It has details that make the story interesting.  For example, instead of saying "They met, they married, he died," a good writer will add more information about the characters.

As a writer, it is hard to resist telling too much.  But it is better to show the reader what is happening.  This makes the story more exciting and engaging.

I watched two news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was on NBC 4 this morning (August 13, 2011). The main story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio who hurt his wife. He is named Shad Hostettler. They showed his picture. He looked very bad. The news spent only two minutes on this story. They said he hurt his wife many times and was arrested. I think they spent the right amount of time on this story.

The second story was about a young man named Travis Buyers, 18. He was shot in Sharon Woods. He was very badly hurt. The police were investigating. They did not find any suspects yet. The police were using a special team to investigate. I think the news was short because the man who was shot was black. I have noticed this before. When a white person is hurt or missing, the news talks a lot. But when a minority person is hurt or missing, the news talks less.

The news also talked about a bullet hole in a helicopter. They said it was shot by a .22 caliber rifle. The police are looking for the person who shot it. They are offering a five-thousand dollar reward for any information.

The news also talked about the weather. They said it will be hot on Saturday with thunderstorms. They said the temperature will be in the mid to low eighties all weekend.

The news also talked about a robbery at a store on Clime Road. The man who robbed the store was black. They said he was wearing a hoodie and was about six feet tall. I think they talked too much about the man's skin color.

The news also talked about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was a big drug seller in Texas. He was convicted of selling a lot of marijuana to Ohio from Texas. They said he was sentenced to 300 months in prison. This is the same as 25 years. I am not sure why they said it this way. They also said he was Hispanic, but this was not important to the story.

Brothers have a special connection. This connection has many feelings: love, pride, and jealousy. They understand each other better than anyone else. When brothers look at each other, they see themselves. 

This connection is strong. It shows itself when brothers are in a difficult situation. This connection can be good or bad. When brothers have strong feelings, they can bring great costs. Understanding brothers is not easy. You must deal with the consequences of their actions. 

When brothers are honest with each other, they see themselves truly. They see their own character. This is shown in a story called "The Scarlet Ibis." In this story, two brothers have a strong connection. They live in a beautiful place with nature all around them. They go on a journey, but it ends in disappointment and sadness. The main character, the protagonist, has many feelings. He feels pride and anger towards his little brother, Doodle. Doodle is very sick and cannot do the things the protagonist wants him to do. The protagonist wants a brother who can play and have fun with him. He is disappointed and even angry with Doodle. But when Doodle smiles, the protagonist's heart feels better. This shows that he loves his brother.

The protagonist's actions come from one main feeling: pride. He wants to teach Doodle, but Doodle is very sick. The protagonist feels sad and angry because Doodle cannot do the things he wants him to do. The protagonist even thinks about hurting Doodle, but then he feels love when Doodle smiles. The protagonist's feelings are very complicated, but they are important for understanding who he is.

The human brain is a complex system. It helps us think and understand the world. A long time ago, people compared the brain to a piece of wax. Then, they compared it to a piece of paper and a book. Now, we compare it to a computer. But these comparisons are not perfect.

The brain gets information from our senses. Our senses are eyes, ears, and skin. They turn physical things like touch, heat, and light into signals. These signals go to the brain. The brain uses these signals to make decisions.

The brain works in two main ways. Bottom-up processing is when the brain puts together small pieces of information. For example, when you look at a black box, the brain puts together the colors and shapes to decide it is a box. Top-down processing is when the brain uses what it already knows to help make decisions. It helps you decide if it is a box or a hole.

The brain also has an attention filter. It decides what signals are important and what to do with them. For example, you might see every blade of grass, but the attention filter helps you focus on what is important.

The brain needs to store information. There are three kinds of memory: sensory, working, and long-term. First, the brain encodes the information. This means it changes the information into a form the brain can understand. Then, the brain maintains the information. For short-term memory, it is like a loop in the brain. For long-term memory, it is like a special kind of protein.

We do not know exactly how the brain stores information. But we have different ideas. Some ideas are based on how people remember things. Others are based on computers and how they work. One idea is that the brain has a network of connections. Each connection is like a link between two ideas. For example, if you think of a chair, you might think of a table and then wood.

Aldous Huxley writes about a bad future in his book Brave New World. In this future, people value group happiness more than individual happiness. From birth, they are taught to want instant happiness. The people are not in control. They are like pawns in a game. A person named the World Controller decides what they should think and do.

Marxist ideas are hidden in the book. Huxley is questioning the power of technology and the way it helps the rich control the poor. He uses words from Marxist ideas, like 'group together' and 'make things seem real'. These words show that Huxley does not like the way the economy is changing.

Huxley also criticizes capitalism. He uses a Marxist idea called 'false thinking'. This means that the common people do not know how the economy really works. They are too busy thinking about their own money and things. The people in charge make them think this way. The lower-class people do not know they are being tricked. They are like robots, always wanting to buy and spend.

In Brave New World, there is no personal freedom. People do not form close relationships. They are like robots, talking only about physical things, not about feelings. The way people act in the book shows how capitalism makes people obey the rules without thinking.

The people in each group are happy with their place in society. This shows how capitalism makes people think they are better than others if they follow the rules and buy things. It is like the Marxist idea of the 'proletariat', the working class people who think they are better than others just because they have money.

I am a student at University Park. I have been here for two and a half years. Getting around campus can be hard for many students. My first year, I lived in an East Halls dorm room. It is very far from the center of campus. To walk to some classes took 25 minutes. This was hard when the weather was bad. 

Years ago, this part of campus was farmland. Now, it has sports fields and new buildings. The campus is getting bigger. This makes it harder to get from one place to another. 

A good solution to this problem is a bicycle. But having a bike is not enough. Students must ride it. The campus must also be safe for bicyclists. 

I talked to a friend who started riding a bike again. He said, "Bikes are great. If you ride a bike, you can get around campus quickly." Biking is good for your body and is the fastest way to get somewhere. I live off campus now. It takes 25 minutes to walk to my classes. But I can ride a bike to class in 5 minutes. 

My bike is very useful. Pollock Road is the best way to get to my classes. But it is not always safe to ride on. Sometimes I must walk to class. If I didn't have a bike, I would have to walk every day. This would take 30-40 minutes. That's 2.5 hours a week. I am very busy. I need my bike to get to class on time.
